      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a speck of dirt. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
