    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a superlative example of the marque\u2019s engineering excellence, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a full VANOS overhaul. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the rear subframe reinforced to exceed factory specifications. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the finish retains its factory depth and luster, free of orange peel or oxidation. The interior is upholstered in Nappa leather with zero bolster wear, and all pixels on the instrument cluster remain intact. This is a mechanically sorted, investment-grade vehicle that offers a pure, analog driving experience with a documented service pedigree.",
