      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence that must be seen to be appreciated. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and presents in absolute showroom condition. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather remains supple and taut, completely devoid of wear or creasing, and still retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature, from the precision navigation system to the ambient lighting, operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using genuine parts. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that bridges the gap between a used car and a brand-new masterpiece. Perfect for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
